in the World, so very exciting.

00:00:35.890 --> 00:00:40.650
And we are very pleased to have
two wonderful food historians

00:00:40.650 --> 00:00:42.800
and chefs here.

00:00:42.800 --> 00:00:47.180
Before I introduce them, I
would like to talk a little bit

00:00:47.180 --> 00:00:50.870
