will also have a nice exhibit

00:01:20.150 --> 00:01:23.170
of our rare books and
special collections.

00:01:23.170 --> 00:01:27.030
So I am Lucia Wolf.

00:01:27.030 --> 00:01:29.510
I work at the European division.

00:01:29.510 --> 00:01:33.960
I am responsible for the
Italian collections, of course.

00:01:33.960 --> 00:01:41.470
