00:12:13.330 --> 00:12:16.260
And talk a little bit about the
evolution of Italian cuisine,

00:12:16.260 --> 00:12:19.120
from the beginning to now.

00:12:19.120 --> 00:12:22.590
And also kind of look
back at the evolution of,

00:12:22.590 --> 00:12:26.060
or how world cuisine has
influenced the food of Italy.

00:12:26.060 --> 00:12:28.840 position:56%
So without further ado, I'd like to,

00:12:28.840 --> 00:12:30.920
for us to get started
on the PowerPoint.

00:12:30.920 --> 00:12:33.590
