00:30:33.080 --> 00:30:34.380 position:56%
It says, I thank you for obliging --

00:30:34.380 --> 00:30:36.220
the obliging act of
your culture of wine.

00:30:36.220 --> 00:30:38.220
And I'm happy to hear
that your plantation

00:30:38.220 --> 00:30:41.240
of them is in so prosperous a way.

00:30:41.240 --> 00:30:44.140
So also, he brought over
people to teach Italian,

00:30:44.140 --> 00:30:45.810
and to start an Italian
studies program.

00:30:45.810 --> 00:30:49.320
So definitely a big
proponent of Italian culture.

00:30:49.320 --> 00:30:51.930
He also smuggled rice into
the United States [laughter],

00:30:51.930 --> 00:30:53.430
from the risotto.

