National festival book, with two
events related to Italian cuisine.

01:03:29.750 --> 01:03:36.380
So, and we thought about why
we can give just a new images

01:03:36.380 --> 01:03:37.680
of Italian cuisine.

01:03:37.680 --> 01:03:43.170
Because the mix of
generation, the mix of culture.

01:03:43.170 --> 01:03:47.100
The mix of people all
over the world.

01:03:47.100 --> 01:03:52.690
And then we have to update
the idea of Italian cuisine.

01:03:52.690 --> 01:03:58.600
In the meantime, we have to
preserve old Italian cuisine.

01:03:58.600 --> 01:04:02.200
And this is another
project that I'm leading.

